<item>
            <title>[LU-1348] Support getattr-by-fid for statahead</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1348</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Originally, statahead thread will pre-fetch directory items (including the attributes) with getattr-by-name one by one, that is inefficient. In the future, we want to pre-fetch directory items with bulk RPC. To simplify the RPC layout and lighten system load, client will use &quot;fid&quot; instead of &quot;name&quot; to pre-fetch attributes from MDT.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
